reviewText: When I got the dvd it wouldn't play .The dvd itself was sticky and had to be cleaned than it would play
DVD did not play at all.
This is long overdue!  I've walked with Leslie for 5 years now, I was ready for a little high-impact.  Love it!
Workout is not bad but I did not feel like I really worked out with this video.  Not horrible but not great.
